T16TD4444E:363b-0: @363b * // 'phrul gyi me long dgu sgor zhes bya ba'i rtsa 'grel bzhugs//
T16TD4444E:363b-2: # // kun mkhyen nyid la phyag 'tshal lo //
T16TD4444E:363b-3: rnal 'byor lta ba'i spyi 'grel brdeg log rtog byang (1) chub yul snang ba'i //
T16TD4444E:363b-4: chos kun (2) sems su gcig mi gcig / lhun (3) gyis grub pa gang la bgyi //
T16TD4444E:363b-5: de nyid snang ba(4) yod dam med //
T16TD4444E:363b-6: ye nas sangs (5) rgyas yin nam min //
T16TD4444E:363b-7: khams(6) gsum sems can ji ltar 'khrul //
T16TD4444E:363b-8: 'khrul (7) pa nyid ni don ci lags //
T16TD4444E:363b-9: rnal 'byor lta (8) ba'i ngo bo gang //
T16TD4444E:363b-10: de dag (9) dogs pa'i the tshom gang //
T16TD4444E:363b-11: de rnams khyad par ji ltar che //
T16TD4444E:363b-12: 'phrul gyi me long dgu skor bzhin //
T16TD4444E:363b-13: gsal byed 'phrul tshig dgu yis ston //
T16TD4444E:363b-14: sgyu ma rnam gnyis spyod yul ni //
T16TD4444E:363b-15: sems kyi chos nyid ngang du gcig / de yi de nyid ji lta ba //
T16TD4444E:363b-16: mkha' dang gzha' snang ji bzhin du //
T16TD4444E:363b-17: log rtog sems rgyud tha dad kyang //
T16TD4444E:363b-18: rigs rgyud med phyir dbye ba dka' //
T16TD4444E:363b-19: sems nyid nor bu rin po che //
T16TD4444E:363b-20: ji ltar dmigs shing sems par snang //
T16TD4444E:363b-22: de ni dngos med kun gyi gzhi //
T16TD4444E:363b-23: log rtog mun pa'i yul snang kun //
T16TD4444E:363b-24: sems phyir mtha' la rtsod pa med //
T16TD4444E:363b-25: gang la yod med med pa lta //
T16TD4444E:363b-26: rtog pa'i smra bsam yul las 'das //
T16TD4444E:363b-27: de ni de phyir rgyal 'gro zhes //
T16TD4444E:363b-28: ris su bcad pa med pa la //
T16TD4444E:363b-29: gtsang dang mi gtsang dngos gcig bzhin //
T16TD4444E:363b-30: phyogs su bltas na nor ba'i blo //
T16TD4444E:363b-32: me long g-ya' dang mkha' sprin bzhin //
T16TD4444E:363b-33: rig dang ma rig gnyis med pas //
T16TD4444E:363b-34: phyogs gcig rkyen gyi dus su 'khrul //
T16TD4444E:364a-2: snang ba nyid na rang bzhin med //
T16TD4444E:364a-3: rang byung phyi nang med snang phyir //
T16TD4444E:364a-4: de dus rang bzhin nyams pa med //
T16TD4444E:364a-5: 'jug pa'i rnam shes de lta bus //
T16TD4444E:364a-6: shes rab thun mong spyan yin no //
T16TD4444E:364a-7: rang byung ye shes tshogs kun bdag / shes rab can gyi mchog yin no //
T16TD4444E:364a-8: rdo rje yid ni dbang mchog phyir //
T16TD4444E:364a-9: lta ba med phyir rang spyi chos //
T16TD4444E:364a-10: dbyer med phyogs lta'i 'dod bral ba //
T16TD4444E:364a-11: ma nor rang gi mtshan nyid rtogs //
T16TD4444E:364a-12: gsum gnyis gcig gis x spangs //
T16TD4444E:364a-13: dang po dngos dang gsal ba dang //
T16TD4444E:364a-14: snga ma sangs rgyas sems can dag / so so sems rgyud tha dad pa //
T16TD4444E:364a-15: gcig na bdun la snga rtogs skye//
T16TD4444E:364a-16: de bzhin sems rgyud brgyad la za //
T16TD4444E:364a-17: tha dad zhe na bdun gyis 'gal //
T16TD4444E:364a-18: de bas dgag dang sgrub med pas //
T16TD4444E:364a-19: gcig dang du ma med pa'o //
T16TD4444E:364a-20: gsum pa'i snga ma rtog skyon dgu //
T16TD4444E:364a-21: phyi ma med pa'i the tshom dag /
T16TD4444E:364a-22: skyon gyi dngos po bcu gnyis shes //
T16TD4444E:364a-23: mi mkhas mkhas pa'i bsam pa ni //
T16TD4444E:364a-24: mi mkhas shin tu mi mkhas pa //
T16TD4444E:364a-25: shin tu mi mkhas mthar lta ba'i //
T16TD4444E:364a-26: mi mkhas yod med rtsod byed cing ;
T16TD4444E:364a-27: / dgag dang sgrub pa gang byed pa //
T16TD4444E:364a-28: de de de la chags sdang skye //
T16TD4444E:364a-29: mkhas dang shin tu mkhas pa ni //
T16TD4444E:364a-30: mkhas pa phal pa dgag sgrub can //
T16TD4444E:364a-31: sgrub pa'i don la brten par byed //
T16TD4444E:364a-32: byis pa'i gzung 'dzin dbang gyur pa'i //
T16TD4444E:364a-33: ma nor lam dang bral ba yin //
T16TD4444E:364a-34: shin tu mkhas pa thams cad la //
T16TD4444E:364a-35: sems phyir dgag dang sgrub pa med //
T16TD4444E:364a-36: de dang rang rig rang snang phyir //
T16TD4444E:364a-37: dgag sgrub bral la yid mi rton //
T16TD4444E:364a-38: de phyir so so dgag sgrub can//
T16TD4444E:364b-0: @364b sgrub pa'i phyogs la zhen pa'i phyir //
T16TD4444E:364b-1: de de med pa ga la mthong //
T16TD4444E:364b-2: de bas rang gi brtags mthong yin //
T16TD4444E:364b-3: de de skas gdang ji lta ba //
T16TD4444E:364b-4: khyad par grangs dang dor ba med //
T16TD4444E:364b-5: cha yod dug la mi 'thung bzhin //
T16TD4444E:364b-6: log lta gnyis su ga la 'gyur //
T16TD4444E:364b-7: gnyis po de ltar de nyid la //
T16TD4444E:364b-8: grub pa'i tha snyad ji ltar mtshon //
T16TD4444E:364b-9: ma grub grub na nges tshig med //
T16TD4444E:364b-10: de ma grub na de bzhin no //
T16TD4444E:364b-11: de bas srid dang mi srid kun //
T16TD4444E:364b-12: lhun grub phyogs su grub pa med //
T16TD4444E:364b-13: bzhi pa'i snga ma skyon drug gnyis //
T16TD4444E:364b-14: de bzhin phyi ma rjes su mthun //
T16TD4444E:364b-15: gnyis med zhe na dus gsum la //
T16TD4444E:364b-16: 'byung zhes bya ba'ang gnyis med dang //
T16TD4444E:364b-17: sman nyid phan gnod bdag gnas ltar /
T16TD4444E:364b-18: ngo bo tha dad 'gyur ba med //
T16TD4444E:364b-19: phyogs las logs pa'i tha dad med //
T16TD4444E:364b-20: lnga pa 'khrul gzhi yod med pa'i //
T16TD4444E:364b-21: skyon ni gsum pa ji bzhin grangs //
T16TD4444E:364b-22: mig yor gsum la dngos med 'dra'i //
T16TD4444E:364b-23: chos yod bzhin pas rang sems la //
T16TD4444E:364b-24: de dngos med kyang rgyu rkyen drug / rang bzhin lhun grub dpag bsam bzhin //
T16TD4444E:364b-25: so sor snang ba dus gsum du //
T16TD4444E:364b-26: rgyun du 'khrul la lhun grub pas //
T16TD4444E:364b-28: gzhi yod med dang dbyer med mtshungs //
T16TD4444E:364b-29: drug pa de ltar de bden na //
T16TD4444E:364b-30: de la skyon du bya ba bdun //
T16TD4444E:364b-33: de bas blang dang dor ba med //
T16TD4444E:364b-34: bde sdug gnas su ris ma blta //
T16TD4444E:364b-35: bdun pa rang rig can yin na //
T16TD4444E:364b-37: de bzhin nyid kyi ye shes 'di //
T16TD4444E:364b-38: mi lnga'i bdag po kun gyi sems //
T16TD4444E:364b-39: rang spyi ji snyed ji lta ba //
T16TD4444E:365a-2: nam mkha' sprin mthongs 'od bzhin du //
T16TD4444E:365a-3: rab rib gang dag shes rab snang //
T16TD4444E:365a-4: brgyad pa des mthong sgrib pa'i grangs //
T16TD4444E:365a-5: brgyad pa bsnyad pa yan lag bcas //
T16TD4444E:365a-6: phyag rgya bzhi yi gzhir gyur pa //
T16TD4444E:365a-7: nges par ngos zin bya bar bsnyad //
T16TD4444E:365a-8: ma rig pa nyid ye shes gsal //
T16TD4444E:365a-9: the tshom nyid kyang nges pa'i spyan //
T16TD4444E:365a-10: log rtog nyid kyang ma nor lam //
T16TD4444E:365a-11: de la mi mthun shes dang bral //
T16TD4444E:365a-13: theg pa'i lta ba gral dgongs //
T16TD4444E:365a-14: skas gdang lta bur bstan pa dag / kun kyang bdag dang bral ba'i phyir //
T16TD4444E:365a-16: de dag nyid ni dgag dang sgrub //
T16TD4444E:365a-17: rim pa yod med khyad par dang //
T16TD4444E:365a-18: ltos pas phye ba'i khyad par ni //
T16TD4444E:365a-19: bdag spong bdag med sgrub pa dang //
T16TD4444E:365a-20: gzugs spong phyi steng sgrub pa dang //
T16TD4444E:365a-21: don 'gog sems tsam sgrub pa dang //
T16TD4444E:365a-22: mtha' spong mtha' bral sgrub pa dang //
T16TD4444E:365a-23: dri spong dag pa sgrub pa dang //
T16TD4444E:365a-24: mtshan 'gog mtshan med sgrub pa dang //
T16TD4444E:365a-25: blang dor 'gog med sgrub pa dang //
T16TD4444E:365a-26: rtsol spong rtsol bral sgrub pa dang //
T16TD4444E:365a-27: de dag kun kyang yod med phyir //
T16TD4444E:365a-28: dgag sgrub rang gis mi byed pa'o ;
T16TD4444E:365a-29: / rim par phye ba'i khyad par ston //
T16TD4444E:365a-30: mthong ba dag dang ma dag pa'i //
T16TD4444E:365a-31: rim pas don gcig khyad par snang //
T16TD4444E:365a-32: mthong ba dge ba'i kun mthong 'di //
T16TD4444E:365a-33: sna tshogs theg pa'i lta ba dang //
T16TD4444E:365a-34: ji snyed bsdom pa'i bya ba rnams //
T16TD4444E:365a-35: spyang bar bya ba ma yin yang //
T16TD4444E:365a-36: ma 'dres yongs su rdzogs par gsal //
T16TD4444E:365a-37: kun shes bzhin 'dra rab rib dri ma nyid //
T16TD4444E:365a-38: bstan pa'i me long mthong goms rang dag sar //
T16TD4444E:365b-0: 'gyur bas ma 'ongs don can @365b ched bgyis pa'i //
T16TD4444E:365b-1: dge rtsas bdag dang mtha' yas 'gro bar bsngo //
T16TD4444E:365b-2: 'phrul gyi me long dgu skor rdzogs so /
